snippet.title: SHORT TRY NOT TO LAUGH CHALLENGE - 10 videos, 10 points - What's your score?
snippet.description:
Here are the rules of this laugh challenge: there are 10 videos, you have 10 points! When you laugh at video clip you lose 1 point! So how many points do you have at the end? I hope 0! Funny animals and pets! Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
